data.title: New Homes In County Durham
data.meta_description: County Durham offers wide open spaces, cities, historic towns and everything in between. Find out why it's the ideal location for your new Persimmon home.
data.text:
County Durham encompasses picturesque towns and villages, stunning landscapes and coastline, and the historic city of Durham. Larger cities like Sunderland and Newcastle are within easy reach, and good transport links make travelling around the UK for work or leisure a breeze. A new home from Persimmon means you’ll be ideally placed to enjoy all that the county has to offer.

Buying a new build home in County Durham

Packed full of history and natural beauty but with its proximity to Newcastle, all the amenities of a modern city are available. Whether looking for rural tranquillity or city living, you’ll find it with a new home from Persimmon.
